    "causal_summary": "Packet 127 closes three P1 items for `deep-agent-improvement`: a hard promotion gate for four-runtime agent mirror sync, explicit partial-runtime-success recovery semantics, and a reusable mirror verification helper. The promotion helper now rejects agent-definition promotion unless `.opencode/agents/`, `.claude/agents/`, `.codex/agents/`, and `.gemini/agents/` all contain the target agent and match the proposed body.",
